# FACET DOC TEMPLATE (EN)

Each facet must have a `.md` documentation file under `/docs/facets/en/{FacetName}.md`.

## Format:
```markdown
# Facet: {FacetName}

### Purpose
Describe the business logic purpose of the facet.

### Functions
- `functionName(params)` — Short description
- `...`

### Access Control
Explain who can call what (UP holders, admin, anyone, etc.)

### Storage
If it uses a library, mention it (e.g. `LibFacetXStorage`).
```

✅ Required before ABI generation.
